---
/**
 * Forward rate comparison chart.
 * Inline brand-tokened HTML/CSS, used in /blog/why-ai-sdrs-are-failing/.
 *
 * Data sources (kept conservative to match the 5-10x claim in the post):
 * - AI SDR baseline: industry median forward rate ~0.1%
 * - Custom Claude Code subagent: median 0.7% on cold B2B SaaS outbound
 *   per the table in /blog/forward-rate-outbound-metric/
 *   (excellent tier reaches 1.5%; median is the honest comparison)
 */
---

<figure class="rate-chart">
  <figcaption class="rate-chart__caption">
    <span class="t-micro rate-chart__eyebrow">FORWARD RATE · COLD OUTBOUND, B2B SAAS</span>
    <span class="t-h3 rate-chart__title">
      AI SDR output rounds to zero. Custom subagents earn shares.
    </span>
  </figcaption>

  <div class="rate-chart__viz" role="img" aria-label="Forward rate comparison: AI SDR industry baseline approximately 0.1 percent, custom Claude Code subagent median 0.7 percent. Roughly 7 times higher.">
    <div class="rate-chart__row">
      <div class="rate-chart__row-label">
        <span class="rate-chart__row-name">AI SDR (industry median)</span>
        <span class="rate-chart__row-value">~0.1%</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rate-chart__bar-track">
        <div class="rate-chart__bar rate-chart__bar--muted" style="width: 7%;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rate-chart__row">
      <div class="rate-chart__row-label">
        <span class="rate-chart__row-name">Custom Claude Code subagent (median)</span>
        <span class="rate-chart__row-value rate-chart__row-value--accent">0.7%</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rate-chart__bar-track">
        <div class="rate-chart__bar rate-chart__bar--accent" style="width: 47%;"></div>
        <div class="rate-chart__bar-tier" style="left: 100%;" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="rate-chart__bar-tier-label">Excellent: 1.5%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rate-chart__axis">
      <span>0%</span>
      <span>0.5%</span>
      <span>1.0%</span>
      <span>1.5%</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="t-micro rate-chart__footnote">
    Forward rate = % of sent messages the recipient forwarded to a colleague.
    Industry AI SDR baseline measured across vendor public reports + 30-day
    campaign audits. Custom-subagent benchmark from active subagent/gtm engagements.
    See <a href="/blog/forward-rate-outbound-metric/">forward rate methodology</a>.
  </p>
</figure>

<style>
  .rate-chart {
    margin: var(--space-12) 0;
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--surface, #141415);
  }

  .rate-chart__caption {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .rate-chart__eyebrow {
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .rate-chart__title {
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .rate-chart__viz {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .rate-chart__row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .rate-chart__row-label {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .rate-chart__row-name {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .rate-chart__row-value {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-h3);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .rate-chart__row-value--accent {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .rate-chart__bar-track {
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .rate-chart__bar {
    height: 100%;
    transition: width 600ms ease-out;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .rate-chart__bar--muted {
    background: var(--muted);
    min-width: 4px;
  }

  .rate-chart__bar--accent {
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .rate-chart__bar-tier {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.4;
    transform: translateX(-1px);
  }

  .rate-chart__bar-tier-label {
    position: absolute;
    left: -52px;
    bottom: -22px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-micro);
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .rate-chart__axis {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-micro);
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .rate-chart__footnote {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .rate-chart__footnote a {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
</style>
